  "img": "icons/svg/mystery-man.svg",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>The youngest Kael and the quietest. Eli never asked to be a hero — it was simply always assumed. His suit, AEGIS-05, reflects what he chose to do with that assumption: it is the stealthiest, most precise unit in the family's arsenal, built for surgical strikes and intelligence gathering. He is the most technically capable of the children after Mira, and the only one who has ever admitted to his mother that he is afraid.</p>",
